title: Supply of creamery butter in Canada 2017
summary: The Supply of creamery in Canada during 2017 showed several fluctuations during the year .
The Supply values have been displayed using Tonnes as unit of measurement .
The most relevant peaks have been recorded during the months of February and June .
gold: The supply of creamery in Canada in 2017 grew rapidly from Jan ( 24000 tons ) to May ( 38000 ) . Then it was stable until July , when it started to drop , reaching 34000 by the end of the year .
